::Prowl::

Prowl screeched again as the noise in his head rose, but then it
stopped and saw IR fall to the ground and revert to her robot mode. He
felt energy and the instincts of his second beast mode drain out of
him, and collapsed on the ground, also transforming to robot mode.

His energy levels were low, but this wasn't the first time this time,
so his systems were already recharging. He slowly gets to his feet,
looking around. He had no idea how he had gotten to this spot.
